title: Looking for a ranked team?

embed.description: Step up your game with a modern voice & text chat app. Crystal clear voice, multiple server and channel support, mobile apps, and more. Get your free server now!

body:
My name is **TitMit**, and I run an unpaid non-sponsored organisation called **ManYx eSports** with a couple friends. If you are looking for a team to play with, please feel free to head to our discord and sign up to become apart of a team! This does not cost anything for you, just head to the sign up forms on the Discord channel and fill everything out, then keep an eye on the **announcements** text channel to see if you've been put in a team.

Please add me, i accept all requests! Summoner Name - _**TitMit**_
